{"tid":1785292,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"（求救）膽粗粗搞咗個中文口試義教，但搵唔到場","createTime":"2019-12-16T09:19:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T04:05:14.000Z","uid":69157,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"f2c089bc1583c0eeef3f237bac8be1b5f8508d8d","tid":1785292,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:19:51.000Z","msg":"事源係咁嘅，之前膽粗粗想出錢出力搞個免費oral義教，本身想租嗰個場太細，容納唔到同時間三十幾人（5組+每組至少1個導師）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。但係搵咗幾日場一係就太貴（&rsaquo;4000蚊6小時）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，一係就未必夠大。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有巴絲能夠<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">借出或建議場地</span></span></strong>就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要求如下：<br />\n時間：1000-1600<br />\n日期：27/12 星期五<br />\n細節：兩小時一節，要有足夠空間令隔離組聲音唔會覆蓋另一組就可以<br />\n人數：每節想有25個同學同5-10個導師。<br />\n<br />\n我會堅持真。義教嘅原則，無大台，我只會準備題目、紙張及相關筆記（唔印補習名，無課程資訊，無廣告）<br />\n所以，如果你有tips想比佢哋都可以聯絡我 tg: <a href=\"https://t.me/tak289312\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftak289312&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7rJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=bb22a16f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tak289312</a><br />\n<br />\n試過聯絡一啲知名少少嘅補習嘅kol想佢幫忙宣傳或者做老師但係無覆到，不過慶幸都有唔少嘅導師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已經有心人願意承擔部分租金<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都多謝巴打先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果可以我都想keep住搞多一兩次，甚至搞埋英文（需要英文神人），幫到越多人越好。<br />\n<br />\n而家報名總人數只有39人<br />\n每個時節（計埋重覆）有20人左右<br />\n<br />\n如果可以唔重覆時節下，理想係幫到75人。<br />\n古語有云：「獨力難以推post」所以幫幫忙，香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n傳送門：<br />\n<br />\n【義教】聖誕免費說話練習<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1779062\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1779062</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"129e20ba6375d5ac400911f17e162d9f524d7b1d","tid":1785292,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:23:10.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"02d0a59c339ac8a8982b31cfb9da922399cbb171","tid":1785292,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:23:20.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"7185291fad523c4a06ae197b5d755047848896fd","tid":1785292,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:23:38.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"27a34462979eaf7fc5dd22f2e428879b2df4efce","tid":1785292,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:23:52.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"2545a213066bd8c7b2789a9f608c968d616fae2a","tid":1785292,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:24:02.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"6130fb28c791482252a0e2b69553c27061a721c3","tid":1785292,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:24:12.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"4581e4db3abe729e4fb0d97efe65d1a0762600cd","tid":1785292,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:24:26.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"bb242f12130553f80137ea7f1f35d3ddb9e866e9","tid":1785292,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:24:38.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"17e490be847ec7a48c83b41f07f44a56464b6cda","tid":1785292,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:24:49.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"0d9978c2cf159ee96c8068eb482d9c989fe23c18","tid":1785292,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:25:02.000Z","msg":"晏就都可以十連成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5230c79e7f12bb2924c7835452ab32fab5feb1bf","tid":1785292,"uid":179362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:25:45.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\"